# Web App Rules

## Data fetching

- Import request/response types and Zod schemas from `@repo/shared` only — no duplicate API interfaces in `apps/web`.
- Use typed API client (`lib/api-client.ts`); parse responses with shared DTO schemas where critical.
- No direct Prisma or database imports in `apps/web`.
- Do not implement UI for an endpoint until its contract exists in `packages/shared`.

## Routes (do not rename without doc update)

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `/` | Search home |
| `/search/[routeSlug]/[date]` | Schedule results |
| `/booking/[scheduleId]` | Seat selection |
| `/booking/[scheduleId]/payment` | Payment |
| `/ticket` | Lookup by passenger # + phone |
| `/dashboard` | User booking history (auth) |
| `/counter/*` | Counter POS |
| `/admin/*` | Admin + reports |

## UX

- Date picker: `min` = today; show loading/error on all fetches.
- Seat map: visual states available / selected / sold / held.
- Guest checkout must work without login.

## Components

- Prefer Server Components for lists; Client Components for seat map and forms with interaction.
